    <span class="article-type">UPDATE NOTICE</span>
    <span class="date-text">24 October 2025</span>

    <h1>Update to Version 1.2.6</h1>

    <p>This update addresses rare cases where user preferences could reset under certain system protection states, ensuring your personal settings now remain safely preserved across reboots, background launches, and device restarts.</p>

    <h2>What’s New</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>✅ Fixed a background protection issue affecting some iOS 26 devices</li>
        <li>✅ Improved launch speed and resource handling</li>
        <li>✅ Enhanced Hub live limit refresh performance</li>
        <li>✅ Minor interface and animation refinements</li>
    </ul>

    <p>For the best experience and continued sync reliability, we strongly recommend updating to 1.2.6 via the <a
            href="https://apps.apple.com/us/app/airlog-pilot-companion/id6503171890">App Store</a> before your next flight.</p>


